summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 4.4°C) and outside temperature (up 3.3°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 9%) and rainfall (up 0.5 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 623 m), light levels (up 3386 lux), and pressure (up 11 mbar).

The past week and month had observable variation in light levels (up 7116 lux) and cloud levels (up 1026 m) when compared to today.
